briefTitle: A Safety and Efficacy Study of Two Japanese Encephalitis Vaccines ChimeriVax™-JE and JE-VAX
officialTitle: A Multicentre, Randomized, Double-blind, Phase III Study of The Comparative Immunogenicity, Safety and Tolerability of Two Japanese Encephalitis Vaccines (ChimeriVax™-JE and JE-VAX®)
summary: The purpose of this study is to determine non-inferiority in seroconversion and to compare the safety and tolerability between ChimeriVaxTM-JE and JE-VAX to the respective homologous virus strain after completion of vaccination course.

primaryOutcome.measure: Number of Participants With Japanese Encephalitis (Homologous Virus) Seroconversion Following Either ChimeriVax™-JE or JE-Vax® Vaccination
